Package: yamlupdater
Title: Used to Update YAML Header from User Values
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Knight", email = "sjgknight@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8709-5780"))
Description: Package is rough set of functions to take a markdown file with YAML header, and provide some functions to update it using user values through overwriting, merging (key-values merged), or combining (add new keys). Not extensively tested and only on single level YAML fields. 
